{"tid":1818890,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「正視聽」無論你係呢個運動做邊一個位 請你入黎睇一睇","createTime":"2020-01-10T10:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T06:17:11.000Z","uid":204656,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3c2393013087fe9b54a7ddd1434e23fe32a76bba","tid":1818890,"uid":204656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:01:49.000Z","msg":"首先我同大家介紹一隻game 佢個名叫 lol 我係一個玩左8年既玩家 佢係一隻可以5v5實時戰略game 係排位實入面大多數玩家都係單排加隨機4人組隊去奪勝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3HzGMiq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3HzGMiq.jpg&h=aff7d869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解我會講起呢隻遊戲呢？因為呢隻game最令難搞既一個地方亦係令最多玩家棄game既地方正正就係呢4個隨機既人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X0u0hsF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX0u0hsF.png&h=4b674944&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你永遠唔會知道果4個人會做D咩 係不可控制 你唯一可以做既野就係做好自己 故己再及人。就正如呢場運動咁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就用5個常見既位黎比大家代入下<br />\n勇武 文宣 freerider  和理非 泛民<br />\n<br />\n就咁睇可能大多屌泛民 屌 freerider<br />\n但真正要做到冇大台都贏其實係唔可以只靠屌 係要比少少屎再多糖 你要知道香港人係食軟唔食硬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出面又講咩勇武做咩搞和理個遊行 文宣不及勇武 freerider不配黃 和理賣勇武冇撚用 泛民人血饅頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對我黎講信唔信都好 心知就夠了 我最多係勸你轉變 我唔會叫你走唔要你 我想贏 我好想贏 我知道打少一個就差好多 我知我敵人係港共高官 黑警 藍絲 黑社會 中共 個個都大佬級難打 就算比左d豬隊友我我都要帶埋佢贏  因為我知道入左場我Quit唔到Game<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Be humble</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊個位置請你地記緊呢隻字<br />\n<br />\n就好似平時我地大大聲屌你老母  同斯文咁講可否如伯母共度一宵咁 客氣D話唔定真係work 又唔係屌狗唔洗咁落力屌既<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"262a8fd8f263dc7c9ea7556aee95d6f054a4e8b1","tid":1818890,"uid":204656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:02:14.000Z","msg":"少少長但都睇曬佢唔該"},{"pid":"a1e7be7cb3a6766ce60196b646e4f08c13f99440","tid":1818890,"uid":204656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:03:14.000Z","msg":"更何況依家係同緊200萬人共鬥  體諒下帶佢一齊行"},{"pid":"dcf7145807d95765b086bc82f560f516b27cd10b","tid":1818890,"uid":204656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:03:43.000Z","msg":"同埋大家要有抗壓能力 耐打能力"},{"pid":"b34da626ca4a83f5f437dcf05ec54dff0e13f74b","tid":1818890,"uid":205482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:03:49.000Z","msg":"agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca0df406f9c37fb648040ec0e27d52d7661c205","tid":1818890,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gi